Internal CSS

INSTRUCTIONS: Update the webpage from the previous exercise to add the styling as Internal CSS and remove the inline CSS.

<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Internal CSS</title>
    </head>
    <body>
    	<p style="color:red;">Hello World</p>
    </body>
</html>


Answer:
<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Internal CSS</title>
    	<style type="text/css">
    	    p {
    	        color:red;   
    	    }
    	</style>
    </head>
    <body>
    	<p>Hello World</p>
    </body>
</html>